thread.title: BRIEF-NQ Mobile Says Formed Partnership Agreement With Hangzhou First Technology

title: BRIEF-NQ Mobile Says Formed Partnership Agreement With Hangzhou First Technology
text:
February 6, 2018 / 1:53 PM / Updated 2 minutes ago BRIEF-NQ Mobile Says Formed Partnership Agreement With Hangzhou First Technology Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
Feb 6 (Reuters) - Nq Mobile Inc: 
* NQ MOBILE INC. ANNOUNCES FURTHER DEVELOPMENTS IN ITS SMART RIDE BUSINESS BY FORMING A PARTNERSHIP WITH HANGZHOU FIRST TECHNOLOGY CO LTD. 
* NQ MOBILE INC - AS PER PARTNERSHIP, HANGZHOU FIRST TECHNOLOGY WILL ASSIST CO IN REDESIGN OF SMART CARS TO BE UTILIZED AS PART OF SMART RIDE BUSINESS Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
